object.name: InputVenueMessageContent
object.description: Represents the content of a venue message to be sent as the result of an inline query.

object.rst_description: Represents the `content <https://core.telegram.org/bots/api#inputmessagecontent>`_ of a venue message to be sent as the result of an inline query.
